John D. Markley Jr., MBA

Age : 51Public asset : 6,247,040 USDLinked companies :  Charter Communications Inc -  BroadSoft Inc -  InterDigital, Inc. 





Summary 



Mr. John D. Markley is Chairman at BroadSoft, Inc.He is on the Board of Directors at InterDigital, Inc. and Charter Communications, Inc. Mr. Markley was previously employed as Managing Member by Bear Creek Capital LLC, an Independent Director by Charter Communications, Inc. /Old/, an Independent Director by Millennial Media, Inc., Venture Partner by Columbia Capital LLC (Virginia), Partner by Finity Holdings, Inc., a Principal by Federal Communications Commission, and a Principal by Kidder, Peabody & Co., Inc.He also served on the board at Softek Software, Inc. and Telecom Transport Management, Inc.He received his undergraduate degree from Washington & Lee University and an MBA from Harvard Business School.



